ActCannabis Act
Food and Drugs Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Concerning Cannabis (Streamlining of Requirements)
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING CERTAIN REGULATIONS CONCERNING CANNABIS (STREAMLINING OF REQUIREMENTS) in order to reduce regulatory and administrative burden faced by licence holders under five priority areas, including licensing, personnel and physical security measures, production requirements, packaging and labelling requirements and record-keeping and reporting.
